# Lawjohara Website

A professional law firm website developed using Laravel, designed to provide a modern and responsive experience for legal services.

## 🌐 Live Demo

🔗 https://lawjohara.com/

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🛠️ Full Admin Panel for managing content
* 📰 News Management System (Create, Edit, Delete)
* 📩 Contact Form for client communication
* 🌍 Multilingual Support (Arabic & English)
* 🎨 Clean and modern responsive design
* 🔐 Secure authentication system

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

* Laravel 10
* PHP
* MySQL
* JavaScript
* CSS

